<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OpenPizzaMap | Coming Soon</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --c-accent: #c0392b;
            --c-text: #1e1e1e;
            --c-bg: #faf7f2;
            --c-surface: #faf7f2;
            --c-border: #d6d3ce;
            --c-muted: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.6);
            --c-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.12);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--c-bg);
            color: var(--c-text);
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        .pattern-bg {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            opacity: 0.85;
            pointer-events: none;
            background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='240' height='240' viewBox='0 0 240 240' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cstyle%3E .s %7B fill: none; stroke: %23d6d3ce; stroke-width: 1.2; stroke-linecap: round; stroke-linejoin: round; %7D %3C/style%3E%3Cg class='s'%3E%3C!-- Slice 1 --%3E%3Cg transform='translate(40,30) rotate(-10) scale(0.7)'%3E%3Cpath d='M15 35 a10 10 0 1 1 0 -20 M15 15 q50 -10 100 20 l -10 15 q -50 -25 -90 -10' /%3E%3Cpath d='M105 35 l -60 85 l -30 -85' /%3E%3Cpath d='M35 60 q 0 20 8 20 t 8 -20' /%3E%3Ccircle cx='50' cy='45' r='7' /%3E%3Ccircle cx='75' cy='65' r='6' /%3E%3C/g%3E%3C!-- Slice 2 --%3E%3Cg transform='translate(170,50) rotate(140) scale(0.5)'%3E%3Cpath d='M15 35 a10 10 0 1 1 0 -20 M15 15 q50 -10 100 20 l -10 15 q -50 -25 -90 -10' /%3E%3Cpath d='M105 35 l -60 85 l -30 -85' /%3E%3Ccircle cx='60' cy='50' r='8' /%3E%3C/g%3E%3C!-- Slice 3 --%3E%3Cg transform='translate(80,160) rotate(45) scale(0.6)'%3E%3Cpath d='M15 35 a10 10 0 1 1 0 -20 M15 15 q50 -10 100 20 l -10 15 q -50 -25 -90 -10' /%3E%3Cpath d='M105 35 l -60 85 l -30 -85' /%3E%3Cpath d='M30 55 q 0 15 5 15 t 5 -15' /%3E%3Ccircle cx='50' cy='40' r='6' /%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
            background-repeat: repeat;
            -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(circle, transparent 10%, black 80%);
            mask-image: radial-gradient(circle, transparent 10%, black 80%);
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 640px;
            padding: 44px 48px;
            background: var(--c-surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: var(--c-shadow);
            animation: fadeIn 0.9s ease-out;
        }

        .title-pre {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.3rem;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--c-muted);
            display: block;
        }

        .status-chip {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid var(--c-accent);
            background: var(--c-accent);
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.14em;
            margin-top: 18px;
        }

        .status-dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.2rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--c-text);
        }

        .tagline {
            margin-top: 1.2rem;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: var(--c-muted);
            letter-spacing: 0.02rem;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(16px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .content::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 48px;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--c-accent);
            margin: 2rem auto 0;
            border-radius: 999px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 32px 24px;
            }

            .title-pre {
                letter-spacing: 0.2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="pattern-bg"></div>

    <div class="content">
        <span class="title-pre">OpenPizzaMap</span>
        <h1>Something worth <br> waiting for.</h1>
        <p class="tagline">We're refreshing the ovens. Check back soon for the next slice.</p>
        <span class="status-chip"><span class="status-dot"></span>Maintenance</span>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
